title: Confirmed case of meningococcal (Hunter New England Local Health District)
text: ( Source : Hunter New England Local Health District) A young woman has passed away in a lower mid-north coast hospital with meningococcal disease. This is the sixth case of meningococcal disease from the Hunter New England region this year.
